  "body": "<!---\r\nThanks for creating a Pull Request 💖!\r\n\r\nPlease read the following before submitting:\r\n- PRs that adds new external dependencies might take a while to review.\r\n- Keep your PR as small as possible.\r\n- Limit your PR to one type (docs, feature, refactoring, ci, or bugfix)\r\n-->\r\n\r\n## 📝 Description\r\n\r\n- Update test packages\r\n- Fix [flaky test](https://github.com/chakra-ui/chakra-ui/runs/6844151604?check_suite_focus=true#step:9:509)\r\n    - `press` and `user-event` utils cause flakiness, so I've replaced it with `@testing-library/user-event`'s `keyboard`\r\n- Resolve [`An update to Checkbox inside a test was not wrapped in act(...)`](https://github.com/chakra-ui/chakra-ui/runs/6844151604#step:9:11) warnings\r\n\r\n## 💣 Is this a breaking change (Yes/No):\r\n\r\nNo\r\n\r\n## 📝 Additional Information\r\n\r\n- https://jestjs.io/docs/upgrading-to-jest28\r\n- https://testing-library.com/docs/user-event/keyboard\r\n- https://github.com/testing-library/user-event/blob/main/src/keyboard/keyMap.ts\r\n",
